post_text:
⚠ If you still have a NHSD iPad and have not yet paid for it, please do so online by Friday! After Friday, the MySchoolBuck store will close: https://bit.ly/MySchoolBucks-iPads
If your purchased iPad has not yet been wiped, it’s likely because
▪ It’s not turned on;
▪ It’s not charged;
▪ It’s not connected to the internet;
▪ The asset tag or serial number was entered incorrectly (If this is the case, you should’ve received an email from our technology team in your student’s NHSD email account); or
▪ It was purchased this week (These devices will be wiped in the coming days)
❓ If you have questions, please reach out to your student’s school or principal directly. Thank you!

